<li>NASA GSFC Special Act Award (2011)
<li>NASA Group Achievement Award (Glory Mission, 2011)
<li>NASA Group Achievement Award (Earth Science Constellation Red Team, 2011)
<li>National Prize of Ukraine in Science and Technology (2010)
<div class="floatright">
<img src="gfx/medal.jpg" style="width:43px;height:75px;border:0" alt="Medal" />
</div>

