<li>NASA Quality Increase Award (2010)
<li>NASA Special Act Award (2010)
<li><i>JQSRT</i> Milestone Paper Award from Elsevier (2010)
<li>Asteroid 22686 (1998 QL53) named "Mishchenko" by the International Astronomical Union (2009)
<li>Habilitation Doctoral Degree in Physics and Mathematics, The Main Astronomical Observatory of the National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine, Kyiv (2008)

<li>NASA Exceptional Scientific Achievement Medal (2008)
