<li>NASA GSFC Special Act Award (2004)</li>
<li>Fellow of the Optical Society of America (since 2003)</li>
<li>Fellow of the American Geophysical Union (since 2003) 
  (<a href="/staff/mmishchenko/pdf/AGU_Press_Release.pdf">NASA Press Release</a>)</li>
