<li>NASA Group Achievement Award (CRYSTAL-FACE Project, 2002)
<li>NASA GISS Peer Award (2001)</li>
<li>NASA GSFC Special Act Award (2001)</li>
<li>NASA GSFC Job Performance Award (2000)</li>
<li>Henry G. Houghton Award of the American Meteorological Society (1999)</li>
<li>NASA GSFC Job Performance Award (1997)</li>
<li>N. P. Barabashov Award of the Ukrainian National Academy of Sciences (1993)</li>
</ul>



